node.text: Life is a series of choices. From something as simple as hitting the snooze button on your alarm this morning, to something as major as deciding to move cities. Every decision works hand in hand with the next to lead you on this personal journey that is your life. There is no right or wrong. It’s all just part of your story. I love you guys and I hope you choose to do something great with your life, I fuckin believe in u ❤️
